&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-http2-max-headers/"&gt;ERR_HTTP2_MAX_HEADERS&lt;/a&gt; — too many headers.&lt;/li&gt;
